 )
 
 require (
 	github.com/anthonynsimon/bild v0.15.0
 	github.com/gorilla/feeds v1.2.0
 	github.com/nicksrandall/prosemirror-go v0.0.0-20170601171447-b0778c4954c7
-	golang.org/x/image v0.38.0
